    "Quantum Mob/ Q3 Symbol", "language" -> "en", "paclet" -> "QuantumMob/Q3",
     "status" -> "None", "summary" -> 
    "PermutationBasis[{\\[Mu]1, \\[Mu]2, ..., \\[Mu]d}] returns the basis of \
the permutation module consisting of n-tuples of d levels (or letters) with \
content (or type) {\\[Mu]1, \\[Mu]2, ..., \\[Mu]d} associated with a quantum \
system of n := \\[Mu]1 + \\[Mu]2 + ... + \\[Mu]d particles of d levels. \
PermutationBasis[n, d] returns an association of the bases of all permutation \
modules associated with a quantum system of n particles of d levels. \
PermutationBasis[{\\[Mu]1, \\[Mu]2, ..., \\[Mu]d}, {s1, s2, ..., sn}] returns \
the basis of the permutation module consisting of n-tuples of d levels with \
content {\\[Mu]1, \\[Mu]2, ..., \\[Mu]d} associated with a quantum system \
{s1, s2, ..., sn} of d-level species. PermutationBasis[{s1, s2, ..., sn}] \
returns an Association of the bases of all permutation modules associated \
with set {s1, s2, ..., sn} of d-level species.", "synonyms" -> {}, 
    "tabletags" -> {}, "title" -> "PermutationBasis", "titlemodifier" -> "", 
    "metadescription" -> "", "windowtitle" -> "PermutationBasis", "type" -> 
    "Symbol", "uri" -> "QuantumMob/Q3/ref/PermutationBasis"}},
